com.parkingtycoon.views.components

Class HudDiagram

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.parkingtycoon.views.components.HudDiagram
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HudBarDiagram, HudLineDiagram, HudPieDiagram

    public abstract class HudDiagram
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for setting up the required systems to show a diagram in the Hud. This is done be rendering the diagram in a separate buffer and returning a texture to the hud. _EXAMPLE_ frameBuffer { shapeRenderer { abstract drawDiagram(shapeRenderer) } } return frameBuffer.texture
